creator: Custodia Inc.
descriptionHtml:
Custodia empowers you to make intelligent business decisions by enabling access to corporate dollars and fully automating the approval process. Real-time validation of your business expense policies are integrated with a corporate credit card to ensure if an expense occurred, it was already approved. The result: the end of expense reports and more time for you to focus on what matters to your business.

The Custodia mobile app is a companion to a corporate card program and allows you to quickly request budget for any type of business expense as it arises.
